title: Police searching for man wanted in death of young juvenile
content:
EL DORADO (KATV) - Authorities are investigating a Thursday evening homicide.
El Dorado Police were called to a home at the intersection of Louisiana Avenue and East Cook Street just before 7 p.m. after a young person was shot.
The victim's identity was not released.
Officials identified the suspect as Shaquille Green, 20.
Any person with any information on Green's whereabouts is asked to contact the El Dorado Police Department at (870) 863-4141.
